rows.label: qst200712_msg0001
rows.name:
No, let go of me! Contrary
to the name, Yumyum is not
actually at all yummy!

rows.label: qst200712_msg0002
rows.name:
Attacked by Ignas? Is
par for course, mo.

rows.label: qst200712_msg0003
rows.name:
He's kind of a friend by now, isn't
he? We should probably help!

rows.label: qst200712_msg0005
rows.name:
Let's save Yumyum, then
we'll talk mushroom!

rows.label: qst200712_msg0006
rows.name:
It might actually taste better
after some light exercise!
